OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FStaying on the cool side with a
OL,7,Fcontinuation of sunny spells and
OL,8,Fscattered showers through Thursday and
OL,9,FFriday. Drier on Saturday with brisk
OL,10,Fcoastal winds. Overnight frosts
OL,11,Fpossible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
